{"title":"搭配风","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":9,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"搭配风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搭配之风刮不够，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮得顾客皱眉头："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买车搭配千斤顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凉鞋搭配乒乓球。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你买好酒搭配烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管你会抽不会抽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买这买那都搭配，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"规定随他有自由。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问卖方他是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是当今乔太守！*"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别的本事他不会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱点鸳鸯是好手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自家亏损全转嫁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管顾客忧和愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要上钩你就上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不上钩你就走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官商嘴脸大家看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底是俊还是丑？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*《今古奇观》中，有篇小说叫《乔太守乱点鸳鸯谱》。乱搭配即乱点鸳鸯也。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易和元 诗  方成 画"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}